text: Ole Bloch Jensen (born 26 February 1943) is a Danish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Copenhagen
